empty political bag. The question now is whether Barak, after a
series of political defections, can cobble together a functioning
coalition before the Knesset, on a three-month recess, reconvenes
in October and makes a final decision on its preliminary vote to
call early elections. (Teepen, Cox News Service) MOVED THURSDAY.
