apparently it's flying off the shelves in Atlanta. A quick story to
explain the new release (and the game) and to explore that it's hot
and why. (Head, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 8.
</P>
<P>
   RECORDER _ The trend of going from analog recording _ tape,
vinyl records, etc. _ to digital _ optical discs, computer chips,
etc. _ continues with the introduction of the TeraOptix CD Video
Recorder. The unit looks and works a lot like a conventional video
recorder, but instead of recording on tape the TeraOptix machine
records on CD-R or CD-RW blank discs. The record MIDWAY-IFYOUGO _
Details on planning a trip to Midway Atoll. (Pousner, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution.)
</P>
