</P>
<P>
   Bread, fruit juices, sandwich meats and hot dogs that lower
cholesterol.
</P>
<P>
   Yogurt, desserts and breakfast cereals that enhance satiety
(sending the brain a message that the stomach's full, even when
it's not).
</P>
<P>
   Breakfast cereals that help with weight loss.
</P>
<P>
   Yogurt that works like an antacid.
</P>
<P>
   Gum and candy that help prevent plaque and tartar buildup.
</P>
<P>
   Beverages that help maintain healthy eyesight.
</P>
<P>
   Canola oil designed to supply vitamin A and maintain good
eyesight.
</P>
