<HEADLINE>
EILEEN CLAUSSEN: MOTHER EARTH VS. GLOBAL-WARMING SKEPTICS  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Business Editors)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 925-word material from The New York
