<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-11 16:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9033 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r s BC-BBN-AURILIA-HNS &LR;      08-11 0693
