the other seems poised to focus as much on beefcake as on leather.
By Chris Reidy. 800 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; SPORTS &LR;   &UR; (s) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   FBN-PATRIOTS-FRIESZ (Smithfield, R.I.) _ John Friesz has been
through three other teams' preseasons before taking part in his
first with the Patriots last year. Minus some details, they have
all pretty much been the same -- until this year. By William Kalec.
</P>
<P>
   BKO-RYAN-COLUMN (Undated) _ It is not exactly privileged
