   EGYPTAIR-DOCUMENTS (Undated) _ Federal safety panel releases
more than 1,600 pages of documents related to the crash of Egyptair
990 off the New England coast. While the NTSB does not make any
conclusions about a crash cause, the documents contain interesting
new information. By Matthew Brelis. 1100 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   EXITSOURCE-SERVICES (Undated) _ Epitomizing how the wireless
Internet market is growing more in specific services rather than
Web-surfing from your phone, eXitsource is offering information
about services available at 20,000 US highway exits. With a few
clicks you can find out every McDonald's, hospital or hotel for the
next 100 miles. By Peter J. Howe. 1100 words.
</P>
