11-Jan. 21; special late season for spikes and does, Jan. 22-Feb.
4. Statewide archery, Sept. 30-Oct. 29.
</P>
<P>
   _ Mule deer: Panhandle, Nov. 18-Dec. 3; Trans-Pecos, Nov.
25-Dec. 10.
</P>
<P>
   _ Turkey: same as deer season in fall. Spring: North Zone, April
7-May 13; South Zone, March 31-May 6.
