his first playing time of the preseason this weekend. Some say he
should forgo his final dead-end season in Kansas City and hang it
up now, but he still has the competitive spirit and wants to stay
on the sideline ... just in case. By Adam Teicher. Story will move
in the ``s'' category.
</P>
<P>
   ROYALS-ORIOLES -- Orioles at Royals, 7 p.m. start. By Bob
Dutton. Story will move in the ``s'' category.
